node.text:
Ready to sweat? Pilates blew my mind! Join me & Vic moving in a new way with Pilates!
.
You can visit her page her ➡️ @victoriapopoff 
.
She’s giving us a FREE month of virtual workouts with her if you use the code “JESSICA” at www.studioVtv.com
.
My outfit is from my upcoming athletic clothing line!! 😍 Can’t wait to share it with you!
.
Who wants more Pilates in their life? When would you go live with us to workout?
.
.
#virtualpilates
#studiovtv
#pilatesforanyone

node.text:
Few fun facts about me:

1. I write left handed but do almost everything else right handed and footed. 

2. My birthday is August 27,1985 which makes me a Virgo.

3. I am second oldest out of 8 siblings.

4. I have one big ear & one small ear. Growing up I always thought it was normal because I thought I had one of my dads ears and one of my moms ears.🤣

5. My ethnicity is 50% Mexican, 25% White & 25% Filipino.

What’s some fun facts about y’all?
